features: Innovative Design: Our magnetic contact paper has a unique design. We are 4 times thicker than ordinary dry erase white board paper and use high quality PET writing film, it also attracts light magnets (such as magnetic alphabets & numbers, magnetic map puzzle, animal magnets set), as well as memos, photos and other small objects, turning any smooth surface into a creative large multifunctional magnetic receiving board.

Easy writing and erasing: This magnetic whiteboard paper for wall writes smoothly and erases easily without leaving any ghosting, even after 60 days.The included marker is water-based and can be erased with a paper towel or board eraser or a rag.

Create Inspiration: we provide three quality markers, a whiteboard eraser and a storage box for you and your kids to be creative and record inspiration. This magnetic paper is suitable for home, kitchen, office, classroom, studio, playroom and more!

Easy Installation: Our magnetic board for wall measures 17.7'' x 39.4'' and comes with a strong self-adhesive backing, eliminating the need for drilling or tools. Simply peel off the backing paper and apply it to a smooth and dry surface. The gridline design on the backing paper helps you accurately cut it to the desired size. The installation process is simple and quick, and the product comes with an installation manual, allowing you to quickly have a convenient magnetic wallpaper.

WARRANTY & TIPS - If you are not 100% satisfied with our magnetic dry erase board paper, please email us before taking any action, we will solve your problem within 24 hours to avoid unnecessary losses. ( Note: Can be firmly applied to wallpaper, latex painted walls and other fragile surfaces, but will damage the wall when removed ).

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: YOUNGJQ Magnetic Whiteboard Paper, Record Your Ideas Anytime! Our magnetic whiteboard paper is your creative world, you can turn it into: metal whiteboard walls, magnet boards, behavior reward chore charts, memory photo walls, travel maps, gourmet recipe menus, memo boards, weekly to-do lists, chalkboards, removable wall charts and more!Self-adhesive magnetic dry erase whiteboard paper can turn many places into magnetic receiving surfaces. It has no borders and brackets, making it a perfect replacement for ordinary dry erase boards and save more space.

Magnetic Whiteboard Decals can also be used in these areas Give this whiteboard paper to your kids. It will become their graffiti wall , letting their imaginations run wild.INFINITE IDEAS :You can DIY with magnetic contact paper: educational walls, preschool boards, scrabble, tic-tac-toe, and also a good alternative to magnetic easels for kids.
Products and Product Accessories Magnetic whiteboard paper * 1Installation Instruction * 1Whiteboard marker * 3Magnetic maker holder * 1 (Magnetic)Whiteboard sponge eraser * 1 (Magnetic)Magnet * 6

Functional Showcase of Magnetic Whiteboard Stickers Easy to write and clean Magnetic dry erase contact paper is made of new high quality PET material, which allows for smooth writing and easy erasing. It is a good idea to renew your old whiteboard! Magnetic Whiteboard Sticker Magnetic dry erase whiteboards have a very high content of iron powder, which can adsorb a variety of lightly magnetic accessories. (such as magnetic alphabets & numbers, magnetic map puzzle, animal magnets set, postcards, photos). Easy to cut The grid on the back of the dry erase whiteboard paper helps to allow you to cut in straight lines, and you can cut out any shape and size you want! Self-adhesive whiteboard paper Self-adhesive magnetic whiteboard paper that can stick to flat surfaces. Whiteboard magnetic wall decal is made of 5 layers of high quality PVC material, smooth surface, smooth writing, more texture than ordinary thin models, erasable.

Please read before purchase: 1, To be honest, the whiteboard paper is not magnetic itself, but contains lots of soft iron material that attracts all light magnetic objects (e.g. magnetic pegs, magnetic letters, etc.), but is not as strong as metal plates or refrigerators and is not suitable for large or heavy fridge magnets. 2, Remember, if you stick it to a fragile surface (such as wallpaper, latex painted walls, white stucco walls), relocating or removing it will damage the surface. In contrast, it is more suitable to be attached to flat and solid surfaces (e.g. ceramic tiles, glass, wood finishes, etc.). 3, This is a self-adhesive dry erase board contact paper with a smooth surface, Not "magnetic sheet" or "refrigerator chore sheet". 4, Please remove the protective film from the whiteboard before use.It is heavier than other styles of dry erase whiteboard paper, we recommend that two people install it together. 5, If you have any questions or problems, please keep in touch through YOUNGJQ-AMAZON.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’m fairly certain this is my first ever Amazon review because I really wanted to talk about how great this product is. I ordered it not really knowing what quality to expect but it’s a lot better than I thought! The roll of magnetic white board is thick and sturdy, but not too think that I couldn’t fit it on the back side of a sliding glass door. It has a pretty strong magnetic hold and the tile letters are so cute! Markers draw very well and erase easily enough for my two year old who has never used an expo or eraser before. So much better than an easel because it doesn’t take up any space. HIGHLY RECOMMEND!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High quality and sturdy; just what I was hoping for.
reviews.reviewText: I wanted to do more than just stick the contact paper to the wall. I had ordered magnetic paint for an earlier project so I painted a square to place the magnetic whiteboard contact paper on top to make the magnet component stronger. I placed painters tape around that and also painted a frame for a nice look but also a place to put the eraser and marker cups on beside the whiteboard. I think it turned out great! The adhesive is holding nicely so far and it seems to be high quality in that when you write on it it also erases without just smearing like some of the cheaper whiteboard surfaces do. It is very thick and feels very sturdy. I have 7 grandchildren so we will see how it holds up.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Hours of Entertainment
reviews.reviewText: This product is so great! Easy to apply onto wherever you’re looking to apply it.
